        <heading>Local Levy and Collection of Taxes</heading>
        <section eId="sec_12_146f">
          <num>12-146f</num>
          <heading>Municipal option to waive interest accrued during periods on delinquent property taxes owed by social or recreational club</heading>
          <subsection eId="12_146f__subsec_c">
            <num>(c)</num>
            <paragraph eId="12_146f__subsec_c__subsec_7">
              <num>(7)</num>
              <content>
                <p>of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986, or any subsequent corresponding internal revenue code of the United States, as amended from time to time; and</p>
              </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="12_146f__subsec_c__subsec_2">
              <num>(2)</num>
              <content>
                <p>Waive any future interest that may accrue during the period of July 1, 2022, to July 1, 2027, on delinquent property taxes owed by any such club.
